DJ MIGGS FOREAL is not selfish with his craft.

 This well-known house music DJ loves sharing his music knowledge with the youth of Mzansi.

 The DJ-turned-teacher (real name Eutrice Motsepe) he is giving youth a life time as he  teaches music at Boston Media Campus in Pretoria.
